item.description:
gpkg - Utilities for the OGC ‘GeoPackage’ Format High-level wrapper functions to build Open Geospatial Consortium (OGC) ‘GeoPackage’ files. GDAL utilities for read and write of spatial data (vector and gridded) are provided via the {terra} package. Additional ‘GeoPackage’ and ‘SQLite’ specific functions manipulate attributes and tabular data via the {RSQLite} package.
Installation Install the latest release from CRAN:
install.packages(&quot;gpkg&quot;) The development package can be installed from GitHub with {remotes}
